comment.text: The "FileCustomFilterEnabled" translation key is used to display the text "Custom filter enabled." in a UI component, likely as a confirmation or indication of the user's settings on the "History" page in an info panel.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Arabic translation uses a combining character (Arabic Combining Mark for Initial, U+064D) which might cause rendering issues in some systems. It's generally best to avoid these unless strictly necessary for specific ligatures.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Remove the combining character: "تم تمكين الفِلتر المخصص."

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word "Հատուկ" (special) is used, but "շարժական" (customizable/adjustable) might be a more accurate translation depending on the context of 'Custom filter'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider using "շարժական ֆիլտրը" instead of "Հատուկ ֆիլտրը" if the filter is customizable.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, the sentence is a bit literal. A more natural phrasing might be preferred, depending on the overall tone of the UI.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider alternative phrasing such as "Ֆիլտրը սեղմված է" (The filter is set).

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The Korean translation contains a non-breaking space character ( ) which might cause display issues.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Remove the non-breaking space: 사용자 지정 필터 활성화됨.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'ເປີດໃຊ້ຕົວກອງແບບກຳນົດເອງແລ້ວ.' while understandable, is a bit literal. A more natural translation might be 'ກຳນົດການກັ່ນຕອງແບບກຳມົດເອີງ' or 'ເປີດການກັ່ນຕອງແບບກຳມົດເອີງ'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ເປີດການກັ່ນຕອງແບບກຳມົດເອີງ

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation contains a non-breaking space ( ) which might cause layout issues.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Replace the non-breaking space with a regular space.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'прилагођени' (prilagođeni) is correctly spelled, but a more common and simpler alternative would improve readability and naturalness.
While 'Прилагођени филтер је омогућен' is technically correct, it's slightly formal for a user interface element. 'Custom filter' often translates to a more direct and simpler phrase.
The Turkish translation includes a non-breaking space (U+00A0) between 'Filtre' and 'etkin'.  This may cause rendering issues and isn't standard for Turkish.
While "Спеціальний фільтр увімкнено" is a grammatically correct translation, it's a bit formal and clunky. A more natural and user-friendly translation would be better.
